 />\n<br />\n大家覺唔覺近1星期好多 post 都係冇任何證據得張 whatsapp 對話圖，下面D人就開始話希望炒車。其他有曬證據同影片嘅 721 831卧底開槍，同之後活動就冇咩人討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再糾纏係太子站有冇死人，點解？<br />\n1. 欠缺實質證據，除非有人認識死者人士行出黎。<br />\n2. 黑警殺完人屍體都一定運去中國啦，唔會留係香港 (相比中國，香港更易被發現)<br />\n3. 就算去圍狗鐵狗屋都一定唔會比到CCTV你<br />\n4. 81歲浮屍都話可疑 (甚至過千正評)，轉移視線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 太多 fake news (警狗強姦... 得張圖冇其實任何證據)，大量資訊轟炸，造成資訊疲勞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">嚴重分散咗其他核彈，甚至整個活動焦點</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「我地都要贏依場仗 先可以全力清算到黑警同政府 輸咗嘅話真相永遠石沉大海 只會清算返我地手足」</span><br />\n<br />\n我地係要贏呀 依家文宣人數 勇武人數都需要增加 雨革就係咁樣而輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=ec5b8921\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"7631801990645cb3a52d34ecf568ebdd4c2c3d5a","tid":1550370,"uid":32932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"612無勇武 送中條例已經過咗<br />\n問吓你屋企人 覺得政府會驚1萬個勇武 定 200萬個普通行完散水既和理非"},{"pid":"f150ba82f3483db41b633d78a3b3de6ad74227fb","tid":1550370,"uid":1315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"893b4f6e2bd646769645a5a6557330dc496179bd","tid":1550370,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25d54891063175faec39ce9b24d305ae896b4bd2","tid":1